title: Mae Tuen, Lamphun
text: Mae Tuen (, ) is a village and "<a href="tambon">tambon</a>" (subdistrict) of <a href="Li%20District">Li District</a>, in <a href="Lamphun%20Province">Lamphun Province</a>, <a href="Thailand">Thailand</a>. In 2005 it had a population of 11,617 people. The "tambon" contains 17 villages.
